Package: uniMatcher
Type: Package
Title: Canonicalise University and Research Organisation Names
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Cascade", "AI", email = "cascade@windsurf.ai", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR_ORCID_ID_IF_APPLICABLE"))
Description: Provides functions to clean, detect language, and match university or 
    research organisation names against a canonical list and a table of known aliases. 
    Includes direct and fuzzy matching capabilities. Also provides a Shiny application 
    for interactive matching and alias management.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
